Invention:  Penicillin
Year:       1928
Inventor:   Alexander Fleming
Country:    Scotland
Category:   Medicine
Description:First antibiotic from mold
Impact:     Saved estimated 200 million lives

Invention:  Internet
Year:       1969
Inventor:   DARPA/UCLA
Country:    USA
Category:   Communication
Description:Packet-switched network connecting computers
Impact:     Became internet; most transformative network ever

